  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "This plot explores the linguistic structure of the questions by analyzing the most frequent tokens and bigrams after removing stopwords. The goal is to identify recurring patterns that characterize extractive QA tasks."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 851,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
