    "### 5.4 Dependency Parsing"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Dependency parsing reveals the grammatical structure of questions. We analyze the most frequent syntactic dependency relations in questions, to understand how questions are constructed syntactically. We also compare the distribution between answerable and unanswerable questions to see if there are structural differences."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 857,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
